(24570, 375, 0, 1, 'Forgotten Son', '', '2010-05-08 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, 'Did you hear a young child crying?\r\nIn the world all alone.\r\nLike a flower, slowly dying,\r\nbefore he''s hardly even grown.\r\n\r\nWill he ever learn to trust anyone?\r\nHow many times can a heart break?\r\nOnly a lonely forgotten son.\r\nHow much will they take.\r\n\r\n**\r\nStill, he hopes that life will get better.\r\nThe storms will fade to brighter weather.\r\nLife is lived with hearts together.\r\nAlone we all just fade away.\r\n\r\nDoes history always repeat itself?\r\nA river running to the sea.\r\nThey always put him up on the shelf.\r\nHow hard must it be?\r\n\r\n\r\nAll he wants is someone to love,\r\njust to make a start.\r\nBut every time he tries to trust anyone,\r\nThey only break his heart.\r\n\r\n**\r\nWith the hope that life will get better,\r\nthe clouds will part for sunny weather.\r\nPut his broken heart together.\r\nalone we all just fade away.\r\n', '', 378, '', '小逸、Mike', '小逸、Mike ', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2010-05-08 18:58:20', '2013-10-07 17:16:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
